=== quiet ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
  ~ [2] copy > static page
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
=== v ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
      |- state  (absent) -> directory
      `- perm   (absent) -> -rwxr-xr-x
  ~ [2] copy > static page
      |- perm         (absent) -> -rw-r--r--
      `- owner:group  (absent) -> pskry:staff
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
      `- check  exit 1 -> exit 0
  + [5] service > restart web
=== vv ===
  ~ [1] dir > sandbox root
      |- dir          state  (absent) -> directory
      `- ensure_mode  perm   (absent) -> -rwxr-xr-x
  ~ [2] copy > static page
      |- ensure_mode   perm         (absent) -> -rw-r--r--
      `- ensure_owner  owner:group  (absent) -> pskry:staff
  ~ [3] symlink > current -> index
  x [4] run > drop a marker
      `- run  check  exit 1 -> exit 0
  + [5] service > restart web
